        <link href="UploadDocDToC.dita#task_grd_sqt_ht" class="- topic/link " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/DToC/AddingXMLIndex.dita" xtrc="link:6;82:58" type="task"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Uploading your XML document to DToC</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">DToC requires XPath information to upload original XML documents. These may changes         depending on how you have structured your document. The below information is for a XML         document that follows the template structure, but we have noted how you can change the XPath         information to match your document. </desc></link>
