        <link href="OverviewDToC.dita#reference_bfm_blm_lt" class="- topic/link " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/DToC/AddingXMLIndex.dita" xtrc="link:8;84:62" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Overview of Dynamic Table of Context</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">The Dynamic Table of Context (DToC) lets users reveal information about their text that     is not necessarily discovered when reading, such as word frequencies. DToC also allows users to     customize their document with annotations and adding tags. </desc></link>
